I was on that Fear raid. This is the first time I have seen this thread. Not having much desire for open raids (been on some long CRs from them), I rarely look here. When we are forming guild raids, we check to see what's up and not under attack. Sorry, but I have never been on a raid -open or guilded- where I heard anyone say, &quot;Hey, someone go check the FV board.&quot; <br>
<br>
I wouldn't mind going back to Fear to help with epics, if enough of EO wanted to go back when Fear respawns. I like helping with quests and epics, even though I don't plan on going for my own epic.<br>
